item.title: Introducing... Rogue Russia: Agents of mayhem
item.description: Last October, the head of MI5 said Russia was on a mission to cause "sustained mayhem" on European streets. It's hard to spot at first, but it is there in plain sight. This is the unpredictable, violent world of the modern Russian intelligence services Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/739cfc71-b7ce-45b1-9285-f3a84a2502b2
